Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:25.78,Kilas,young Rika,0,0,0,,Ada pegunungan, kepulauan, dan istana juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:29.19,Kilas,young Rika,0,0,0,,Aku suka! Kira-kira seperti apa kotanya, ya?
